reviewText: Burned DVD, not a licensed copy.
Don't buy this version. DVD-R garbage.
Don't fall for this like I did. This is a DVD-r not a legitimate DVD. The cover looks like it was made with a home printer. My DVD players all say unable to read disc. I'm glad it was under 7$.
Straight out of the 70's and loved it...campy and cheesy and worth the time spent watching.  If you are a fan of video from across the pond, recommend.
